node.text:
Compilation of my best flips and tricks from the past couple of years 🔥😂 Keep an eye out for part 2&3 soon!
Song: Blackbear - 4U ( @bear )
.
I want to tell you a random thing about myself that you probably don’t know (unless you have met me in person). It might come as a surprise, but I am an introvert and I struggle with anxiety. It has improved over the years, but I still struggle sometimes and I’m still finding ways I can deal with it. 
Anyway, I basically just wanted to say that it doesn’t matter how different you are. A lot of people told me that I would NEVER get to where I am now because of the way I am. But I stuck with it, and it worked out in the end!
It’s good to listen to the constructive feedback. But ignore the destructive. Or use it as fuel!
Anything is possible.
I’ll stop being cringy now 👌🏼😂
#nevergiveup #acrobatics #flips #gymnastics #parkour #freerunning #introvert #circus #fitness #motivation #anxiety #trainhard #physicalcomedy #martialarts #tasmania #australia
